original_title: Universal Ike Junior Nearly Gets Married
overview: Young Ike has fallen for the rancher's daughter. His chances improve when it's found that he stands to inherit $50,000, but things get complicated it turns out that he's actually $50,000 in debt.
tagline: Thinking Ike is the old woman, Susie doses him with castor oil.
title: Universal Ike Junior Nearly Gets Married
